HB 216 Original 2026 Regular Session Robby Carter
Abstract: Authorizes counsel of record to elect a preferred method of service.
Present law (C.C.P. Art 1313(A)) provides service may be made by mail, delivery, or
electronic means.
Proposed law retains present law and provides that counsel of record may elect a preferred
method of service.
(Adds C.C.P. Art. 1313(E))
